window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Is she alive, or is she missing for good?</p> <p>When the estranged daughter of Scotland's premier art dealer goes missing, Private Investigator Hanlon is hired to find out where Aurora is.</p> <p>But what she thinks will be a relatively straightforward job soon turns dangerous. The missing girl has a troubled past, but what made Aurora suddenly pack her bags and disappear?</p> <p>Hanlon has her work cut out for her. The stakes are rising, and she needs to get to the bottom of the case before someone else is attacked.</p> <p>And is Aurora still alive, or is she missing for good?</p> <p><b>A gripping new case for feisty female Private Investigator Hanlon. Perfect for fans of Angela Marsons, Robert Bryndza and Lisa Regan.</b></p>"; 
